    "body": "At some point between the 2013 and 2015 releases we switched from using SDL 1.2 to the newer SDL 2.0 series.  We haven't seen any similar bug reports, so I suspect that the problem is with the SDL2 packages in your OS.  Unfortunately the 12.10 releases of ubuntu are no longer supported, so you may have to upgrade to a newer OS in order to solve this.\n"
